commit.message: Convert README to Markdown format

build: use pkg-config to find imlib2

imlib2 1.7.5+ drops imlib2-config, hence pkg-config
must now be used to find it.

Bug: https://bugs.gentoo.org/828962
Closes: https://github.com/neagix/idesk/issues/7

Version 0.7.8

Updated changelog and version
Add docker images for building and previewing/testing

Do not fail starting idesk if an icon file is invalid or cannot be loaded

Use stderr for messages
Reintroduce SVG support via librsvg
Prevent out of bounds error by checking index
